metadata.description:
Uncanny Valley is a common unsettling feeling people experience when androids (humanoid robots) and audio/visual simulations closely resemble humans in many respects but are not quite convincingly realistic.

I am terrified and excited by the advance of Skynet representing art, my head explodes to imagine what's next? it's time to take a step forward.
